HEADWORD: Mesmerize
<hw>Mes"mer*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Mesmerized</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
